version_description: Updates made to improve app performance.
Updates made to improve app performance.

Our latest update includes:

Continued enhancements to our mobile deposit experience.
- General bug fixes and performance improvements.

You asked and we’ve listened.

Introducing Transfer & Pay, providing new ways to manage transfers and bill payments from your mobile phone. You can now:

- Set up, view, and edit recurring transfers and bill payments.
- Edit and delete your bill payment account information and recipients.
- Make payments to Fifth Third Bank Credit Cards and Loans from accounts held at other banks.

You asked and we’ve listened.

Introducing Send Money with Zelle℠ a new way to pay friends and family in minutes. Enable Siri and send money with Zelle℠ using only your voice.

In addition, this update introduces “Offers & Products,” allowing you to view available offers and personalized recommendations, or quickly open new products right from our mobile app.

- Find everything you need faster with updated navigation and intuitive visual display.
